@inherits GameRulesBase

<p>
    <b>Rules</b>: players take turns dropping discs into a 7x6 grid; a disc falls
    to the lowest empty cell of the chosen column. The first player to connect
    4 of their discs in a row (horizontally, vertically, or diagonally) wins.
    See <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Connect_Four">Connect Four on Wikipedia</a>.
</p>
